{"tid":847943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特衰護照轉 BNO 有乜要留意？","createTime":"2018-10-04T14:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T14:53:52.000Z","uid":7632,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"70f820bd57716655db182f3bf0496a0be2e06761","tid":847943,"uid":7632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:11:56.000Z","msg":"本人有未到期特衰護照，最近亦成功續領 BN(O)，請問，如果入境美帝，唔用用開嘅特衰護照，轉用BN(O)，會唔被Customs and Border Protection啲 Staff起疑，因先前所有入境嘅declaration forms (6059B)都係用之前本特衰護照，未用過新嘅BN(O)<br />\n<br />\n係咪訂機票用特衰護照號碼，就最好用特衰入境？<br />\n下次用BN(O)訂機票，先用BN(O)入境？<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有經驗？<br />\n<br />\n利申：再申請BN(O)事關美帝會越來越對支那收緊入境政策，怕殃及池魚，連特衰護照都抄車，所以申請BN(O)，用BN(O)入美帝境啫"},{"pid":"3749b982740f97901ff70a6402691a4f9012c2f9","tid":847943,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"自己SEARCH BNO薪火相傳POST啦"},{"pid":"53d37bbf2c666290f6d7fe2061d5743ccdc63b41","tid":847943,"uid":30788,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:39:24.000Z","msg":"點解你篇野好似有陣柒味怪怪地咁"},{"pid":"0b2eb143c6bb0ace3971b53ca9f692b365ec21a0","tid":847943,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:40:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7fdc34815bf4d6177a4e613b04df4c940101d089","tid":847943,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b2eb143c6bb0ace3971b53ca9f692b365ec21a0","tid":847943,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:40:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:43:03.000Z","msg":"對VISA"},{"pid":"abeff273d221c8f504ff4219472f0b4fcd235de7","tid":847943,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a69dd051b4db340a60921ed51d4c47be13a11643","tid":847943,"uid":10398,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T14:45:52.000Z","msg":"你申請美帝visa時用咩passport就要用果本啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\"